item.title: I realy realy realy need help compiling
item.dc:creator: @udluv2 udluv2
item.description:
@udluv2 wrote:

go to ur source foler and right click on compiler and click edit then delete everything in then and add this:

@echo off COLOR 08 title Doublescape Client "C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.5.0_06\bin\javac.exe" -cp . *.java "C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.5.0_06\bin\java.exe" server pause

U can change Doublescape to ur server name.

Hope this helps
